sec.p:
It is well known that the French worker, Sabatier, over a Century ago, demonstrated how methane could be produced synthetically by passing a mixture of CO2 and H2 over a supported Ni catalyst:CO2+4H2→CH4+2H2O\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
